  Add ree18 support

*rubygems-0-r2 (31 Jan 2010)

  31 Jan 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +rubygems-0-r2.ebuild:
  New virtual that uses rubygems[jruby] to provide RubyGems on JRuby.

  11 Jan 2010; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> rubygems-0.ebuild,
  rubygems-0-r1.ebuild:
  Set empty HOMEPAGE and LICENSE.

  01 Jan 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> rubygems-0.ebuild,
  rubygems-0-r1.ebuild:
  Null out all the functions to avoid that those from ruby-ng will actually
  be executed (waste time).

